Comparator&lt;Character&gt; lettersFirst = 
    Comparator.comparing((Character ch) -&gt; Character.isDigit(ch))
              .thenComparing(Comparator.naturalOrder());

chars.sort(lettersFirst);
System.out.println(chars);
```
